    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<hr />

<h2>Kite Lines</h2>

<p>Line length controls the kite's arc — longer lines = larger sweep = more power generation per stroke. In stronger wind, shorter lines reduce power and increase control.</p>

<div class="not-prose mb-6">
  <table class="text-sm w-full text-gray-300 border-collapse">
    <thead>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
        <th class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">Length</th>
        <th class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">Wind Range</th>
        <th class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">Paired With</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">26m</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">12-15 kts</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">5.0m kite — max arc for light wind</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">25m</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">14-18 kts</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">4.0m kite</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">24m</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">15-22 kts</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">3.4m or 2.2m kite — standard trades</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">22m</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">22-25 kts</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">2.2m kite — start depowering</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">18-20m</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">25-30 kts</td><td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">2.2m kite — strong trades</td></tr>
